{"tid":2451132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國商務部向多家中國通訊公司發傳票  調查國安風險","createTime":"2021-03-18T01:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T06:39:06.000Z","uid":227801,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2092514692705fe3e77aae56e87225e61aeb91fc","tid":2451132,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T01:32:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103180008.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202103180008.aspx&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2RphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=9957a336\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103180008.aspx</a><br />\n（中央社華盛頓17日綜合外電報導）美國商務部今天表示，已向多家在美國提供資訊與通訊技術服務的中國企業發出傳票，以調查它們是否構成國安風險。<br />\n路透社報導，商務部長雷蒙多（Gina Raimondo）透過聲明表示：「北京涉入削弱我國科技優勢、威脅我國盟友的舉動。」<br />\n聲明並指出，當局將透過這些傳票蒐集資訊，「以便於我們採行最能保護美國企業、美國工人與美國國家安全的可能行動」。<br />\n這份聲明並未點名任何公司。但美國前總統川普（Donald Trump）政府曾鎖定中國電信巨擘華為技術公司（Huawei Technologies）和中興通訊（ZTE Corp），要美國電信基礎設施移除它們的設備。（譯者：楊昭彥）1100318"},{"pid":"5e6383761b9924f110adac8db1565ef247a3ecbd","tid":2451132,"uid":2419,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T01:34:10.000Z","msg":"維護國家安全好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed6cef606c24b51d18ed705897e067874f5e7cc","tid":2451132,"uid":227801,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T01:34:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/fcc-to-revoke-chinese-telecom-license-20210317/5819067.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Ffcc-to-revoke-chinese-telecom-license-20210317%2F5819067.html&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2RphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=7a29de0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/fcc-to-revoke-chinese-telecom-license-20210317/5819067.html</a><br />\n美國政府開始撤銷兩家中國通訊​公司在美國提供通信服務的經營權。<br />\n美國聯邦通訊​委員會星期三（3月17日）表示，已經開始撤銷中國聯通美洲公司（China Unicom Americas）和太平洋網絡有限公司（Pacific Networks）及其全資子公司ComNet在美國提供州際和國際通訊​服務授權的程序。<br />\n聯邦通訊​委員會去年4月發布命令警告說，可能關閉中國聯通美洲公司、太平洋網絡有限公司和中國電信（China Telecom Corp Ltd）這三家中國國營通訊​公司在美國的運營。中國聯通在美國的經營權已經有20年，在美國提供國際通信服務。<br />\n聯邦通訊​委員會去年12月開始撤銷中國電信這家中國最大通訊​公司在美國提供通訊​服務授權的程序，這項授權已經有將近20年的歷史。<br />\n聯邦通訊​委員會專員斯塔克斯（Geoffrey Starks）表示，很多中國通訊​運營商&ldquo;也擁有在美國國內經營的數據中心，&rdquo; 聯邦通訊​委員會目前缺乏&ldquo;解決這個潛在國家安全威脅的授權。&rdquo;<br />\n聯邦通訊​委員會2019年5月投票一致決定拒絕給予中國移動（China Mobile Ltd）在美國提供服務的經營授權，理由是中國政府可能利用這項授權對美國政府從事間諜活動。<br />\n（本文依據了路透社的報導）"},{"pid":"df081a518606badf37063f5c3248d294875ecf4d","tid":2451132,"uid":227801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T01:37:07.000Z","msg":"美商務部向多間中國通訊供應商發傳票　FCC啟動程序阻聯通、ComNet在美經營<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部向多家中國通訊供應商發出傳票，作為對潛在國家安全風險進行審查行動的一部分。聲明中沒有公布向哪些公司發出了傳票。商務部稱，傳票是收集信息，為確定保護美國企業及工人安全而可能採取的行動的重要步驟，希望受審查的公司合作。<br />\n另外，美國聯邦通訊委員會（FCC）據報將啟動程序，料阻止中國聯通（香港）及ComNet在美國開展經營活動，指相關公司因受中國政府控制而存在安全風險。<br />\n聯通&nbsp;（00762）&nbsp;回應指，該公司通過完全合法的子公司已經在美國市場運營接近20年，其期望FCC能夠對公司的行為進行徹底，公正和基於事實的檢視。<br />\n<br />\n此前，FCC據2019年通過的法例，將內地5家企業列入危害美國國家安全的名單內。列入制裁名單的企業分別為華為、中興通訊&nbsp;（00763）&nbsp;、海能達、杭州海康威視、大華科技。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nhttps://inew<del><a href=\"http://s.hket.com/article/2904380/%E7%BE%8E%E5%95%86%E5%8B%99%E9%83%A8%E5%90%91%E5%A4%9A%E9%96%93%E4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2904380%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%258B%2599%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%25A4%259A%25E9%2596%2593%25E4&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2RphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=091f89bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">s.hket.com/article/2904380/%E7%BE%8E%E5%95%86%E5%8B%99%E9%83%A8%E5%90%91%E5%A4%9A%E9%96%93%E4</a></del><del>%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E5%95%86%E7%99%BC%E5%82</del>%B3%E7%A5%A8%E3%80%80FCC%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E9%98%BB%E8%81%AF%E9%80%9A%E3%80%81ComNet%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E7%B6%93%E7%87%9F"},{"pid":"7ffeb809faded3a337ecc50dffe45f832f68fc79","tid":2451132,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T01:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353184762fee8303485ee90695b7cac9e0e268ea","tid":2451132,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T01:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92704cfd916bb6b9a8f734acc621989aa7547f26","tid":2451132,"uid":84128,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T01:47:07.000Z","msg":"Trump: we are best fd<br />\nJoe: I forget it"},{"pid":"f36cfa98f0c96a6d5c8ef72f788269cb3812aa84","tid":2451132,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T01:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095704d7d62f00671d6b8ac2a5d599a909895bce","tid":2451132,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b45e1cdb79baf2e48093ab57dbdc4954df92b6","tid":2451132,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d669a56ee37924c0cbb29ee8e1cf65cb58bf7d8c","tid":2451132,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:15:14.000Z","msg":"維護國家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國安法好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9989dec4b15306e4cd3d2a9216575e13dce0b7d","tid":2451132,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa9cc509c2ca83fdc369144e8d98b2d5a4d4414","tid":2451132,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251a990033e03d22fbb02a5b37ebf1c202a714d3","tid":2451132,"uid":337119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:42:27.000Z","msg":"堅決維護美國國家安全！"},{"pid":"d300e06ad62aaf3ab7473526bc5d3811f046b78e","tid":2451132,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"251a990033e03d22fbb02a5b37ebf1c202a714d3","tid":2451132,"uid":337119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:42:27.000Z","msg":"堅決維護美國國家安全！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:44:22.000Z","msg":"國家安全是頭等大事，市民安居樂業基礎，維護國家安全是美國政府責任"},{"pid":"b37c1db9fa31f96f3d0e443011c01df147e007ee","tid":2451132,"uid":36004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解要咁樣對中資企業，公平咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea76c1700b219a24e593c9f584d0d9eda4df6c5","tid":2451132,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"251a990033e03d22fbb02a5b37ebf1c202a714d3","tid":2451132,"uid":337119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:42:27.000Z","msg":"堅決維護美國國家安全！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:51:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9cb5d9389800c8bff653450e4935f3972268dc","tid":2451132,"uid":394702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zmw4EfT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZmw4EfT.jpg&h=a7ba86ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9e36172dc5d470fd004e71033318bec1a73ae4b","tid":2451132,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T03:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55fa9172e9dbdaf40c601996a05adddf1fb812c2","tid":2451132,"uid":394702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T03:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d92027eaf768ccc005243390716d241f1d6073","tid":2451132,"uid":394702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T03:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a1f019c9b4b701e2fcc06b8a50ee7d5706908d","tid":2451132,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T03:24:33.000Z","msg":"Harris 做到嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279d4f80f997d53bf2d90226e6e89368e8ac21e4","tid":2451132,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T03:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0dc59930cd765ab1be04974ea6f4d3523c3ac53","tid":2451132,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F06%2F20201506_PO_%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD.png&amp;h=e665866f&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"94cc93058b7b4a5907e0035ac7959460cf69270e","tid":2451132,"uid":9069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:52:52.000Z","msg":"外交部會唔會出黎話<br />\n<br />\n美國市場號稱所謂自由開放，中方對美方以國家安全為名針對中國企業表示十分憤怒。中方將強硬回應。"}],"pinned":{"pid":"6ed6cef606c24b51d18ed705897e067874f5e7cc","tid":2451132,"uid":227801,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T01:34:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/fcc-to-revoke-chinese-telecom-license-20210317/5819067.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Ffcc-to-revoke-chinese-telecom-license-20210317%2F5819067.html&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2RphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=7a29de0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/fcc-to-revoke-chinese-telecom-license-20210317/5819067.html</a><br />\n美國政府開始撤銷兩家中國通訊​公司在美國提供通信服務的經營權。<br />\n美國聯邦通訊​委員會星期三（3月17日）表示，已經開始撤銷中國聯通美洲公司（China Unicom Americas）和太平洋網絡有限公司（Pacific Networks）及其全資子公司ComNet在美國提供州際和國際通訊​服務授權的程序。<br />\n聯邦通訊​委員會去年4月發布命令警告說，可能關閉中國聯通美洲公司、太平洋網絡有限公司和中國電信（China Telecom Corp Ltd）這三家中國國營通訊​公司在美國的運營。中國聯通在美國的經營權已經有20年，在美國提供國際通信服務。<br />\n聯邦通訊​委員會去年12月開始撤銷中國電信這家中國最大通訊​公司在美國提供通訊​服務授權的程序，這項授權已經有將近20年的歷史。<br />\n聯邦通訊​委員會專員斯塔克斯（Geoffrey Starks）表示，很多中國通訊​運營商&ldquo;也擁有在美國國內經營的數據中心，&rdquo; 聯邦通訊​委員會目前缺乏&ldquo;解決這個潛在國家安全威脅的授權。&rdquo;<br />\n聯邦通訊​委員會2019年5月投票一致決定拒絕給予中國移動（China Mobile Ltd）在美國提供服務的經營授權，理由是中國政府可能利用這項授權對美國政府從事間諜活動。<br />\n（本文依據了路透社的報導）"}}